              <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-green-600">2</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-dark-900 mb-3">Customization & Setup</h3>
            <p class="text-dark-600">Customize Odoo ERP to fit your company operations and setup required modules</p>
